{"word":"Hivites","slug":"hivites","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hivites</b> A tribe of Canaanites.<br/> General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=17'>Gen 10:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=15'>1Ch 1:15</a><br/> Shechemites and Gibeonites were families of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=34&verse=2'>Gen 34:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=7'>Jos 9:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=19'>Jos 11:19</a><br/> Esau intermarries with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=34'>Gen 26:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=2'>Gen 36:2</a><br/> Dwelling place of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=3'>Jos 11:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=3'>Jdg 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=7'>2Sa 24:7</a><br/> Their land given to the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=23'>Exo 23:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=28'>Exo 23:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=17'>Deu 20:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=5'>Jdg 3:5</a><br/> Conquered by Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=1'>Jos 9:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=8'>Jos 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=11'>Jos 24:11</a><br/> Pay tribute to Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=21'>1Ki 9:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=8'>2Ch 8:8</a>"}]}